      "in_reply_to": null,
      "unresolved": true
    },
    {
      "id": "56cff4fd_7de84bcf",
      "file_path": "k6-tests/make-logs.sh",
      "patchset_number": 5,
      "line": 29,
      "message": "Lets break it down: cps-cps-and-ncmp-cps\n\n1st part (cps-): is necessary since we only support one deployment name at the moment. (helm install cps ../cps-charts). Let's keep it. (the 3rd parameter)\n\n2nd part (cps-and-ncmp): can be changed, it is always binded from _helpers.tpl .\nI suggest to change this template to \"ncmp\" only!\n\n3rd part (-cps): can easily be removed. it does comes from the cps-deployment.yml through metadata -> name suffix.\n\n\nSo eventually, the service name become \"cps-ncmp\"\n\nThe other services would become: cps-ncmp-dmi-stub, cps-ncmp-postgresql",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 8063,
        "name": "Halil Cakal",
        "display_name": null,
        "email": "halil.cakal@est.tech",
        "username": "halil.cakal"
      },
      "updated": "2025-10-14 11:04:12.000000000",
      "in_reply_to": "bcae2c04_bf8628b3",
      "unresolved": true
    },
